high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room then hang a left and walk up to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Slice up the head of lettuce that is on the counter in front of you.
Put the knife on the front left edge of the counter.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the lettuce inside the lower compartment, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the door and take the piece of lettuce out and then close the door.
Turn right and begin walking across the room then hang a right and walk over to the small silver bin in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled piece of lettuce in the back left corner of the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of lettuce in a silver bin.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the counter in between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of the lettuce.
Slice the right lettuce into small slices.
Place the knife back on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right, walk towards the wall, and then turn left towards the grey bin on the floor.
Place the lettuce in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of lettuce in the grey bin.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and walk to the counter between the refrigerator and the stove.
Pick up the knife by the lettuce from the counter.
Slice the left half of the lettuce that is on the counter.
Roll the right side of the  lettuce toward the stove.
Pick up the rightmost slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator. Place the lettuce slice on the top shelf,and shut the door. Open the door and grab the lettuce. Shut the door.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn right, and walk to the counter by the waste basket.
Throw the lettuce into the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Toss cooled lettuce into the waste basket.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the counter tops next to the stove.
Take the knife on the counter on left of the stove.
Cut the cabbage on the counter into 3 pieces.
Place the knife in front of the black sauce pan on the counter.
Take one piece of cabbage.
Take the cabbage piece to the refrigerator on the left.
Chill the cabbage in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around and take the chilled cabbage piece to the gray plastic bin in the corner across the room.
Place the cabbage into the plastic bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a piece of chilled cabbage.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the sink and walk to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife from under the head of lettuce.
Slice the head of lettuce into pieces.
Put the knife down on the left side of the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter top.
Turn left and walk to the fridge on your right.
Put the lettuce inside the fridge, let it chill seven seconds and remove the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn right, head to the wall and hang a right to reach a tall gray container on the floor.
Place the chilled lettuce slice to the left of the potato inside the container.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce in a container.
